OL,3,CBen Stokes reports for duty with
OL,4,CDurham after England Test squad
OL,5,Comission
OL,7,FEngland cricket captain Ben Stokes
OL,8,Freported for duty today (Friday) as he
OL,9,Fprepared to return to action for
OL,10,FDurham.
OL,12,FThe 35-year-old has been stood down
OL,13,Ffrom second Test duty against New
OL,14,FZealand at the Oval ` along with
OL,15,Fbowler Gus Atkinson. It's as a breach
OL,16,Fof team protocols following the first
OL,17,FTest victory over the Kiwis at Lord's
OL,18,Fis investigated. Stokes arrived at the
OL,19,FBanks Homes Riverside ground at 8.40am
OL,20,Fahead of the scheduled start of play
OL,21,Fat 11am.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
